api_name = 'temp-unit-test-api'
path = '/'
method = 'POST'
api_id = self.api_gateway.rest_api_create(api_name).get('id')
resource_id = self.api_gateway.resource(api_id, path).get('id')
self.result = self.api_gateway.method_create(api_id, resource_id, method)
assert method in self.api_gateway.resource_methods(api_id, path)
self.result = self.api_gateway.method_delete(api_id, resource_id, method)
assert [] == self.api_gateway.resource_methods(api_id, path)
self.api_gateway.rest_api_delete(api_id)
